overview: Roberto is on the run after committing a crime of passion. But his sins come back to haunt him... because he's just met a very wrong girl... on a very wrong night... on a very wrong side of town. It's Wave's Jenna Jameson and Rocco Siffredi... together finally in Jenna Loves Rocco, a Toni English film. It's about Rocco and Jenna, Brooke and Bobby, and Anna and Alex. It's about the night they'll never forget. Now in a film you'll never forget.
title: Jenna Loves Rocco
